    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong> into wedges and set them aside for garnish</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
