    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), a squeeze of <strong>lime</strong> juice, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>lime mayo</strong></p>",
